storyText1: I'm a Software Engineer from Seattle, WA with experience across the stack, but a passion for the Front End. I'm currently looking for a new role, most recently having worked as a Software Engineer II, Core Platform Team at Bttn. I love finding creative solutions to complex problems and creating beautiful, reliable, and responsive web applications.
storyText2: When I'm not coding, you can find me spending time with my dogs, listening to music, going to see live music, reading, watching hockey, or clumsily playing hockey in the Kraken Hockey League.
